summary:
It's pretty simple mod. Whenever you stealth attack someone "Oh baby a Triple!, oh Yeah!" will be played. Copy data folder to your skyrim folder. If you want to uninstall just delete file. Path is:
Data/Sound/fx/ui

Oh and if you want other MLG sound to it just ask in comment
